{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317790/extras/0.gif?t=1736668511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of Agent Kim, a hardened private investigator drawn into a chilling mystery in the heart of a forsaken wilderness. For over 20 years, nine souls have vanished without a trace from a secluded, eerie villa, including your client\u2019s fearless relative, Mr. Lin. With the police powerless to uncover any answers, it falls to you to confront the darkness shrouding this cursed place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317790/extras/7.gif?t=1736668511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upon slipping into the villa under the cover of night, you are struck down by an unseen force. You awaken in a cold, desolate room, and a terrifying truth dawns\u2014you are the latest prisoner of this accursed mansion. The air hangs thick with dread, and every shadow conceals a new threat as the undead prowl the darkened halls. Your only hope lies in a desperate race against time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317790/extras/8.gif?t=1736668511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, experience the core gameplay and the gripping opening chapters of <i>Mansion of the Dead</i>. Test your nerves as you scour the villa for keys to locked doors, decipher cryptic clues to crack safes, and wield strange tools to unravel the secrets of a long-forgotten underground chamber.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317790/extras/6.gif?t=1736668511\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you escape the darkness, or will you join the lost souls who vanished without a trace?</p>","background":"https://shared.ak